children.text: Low pitch, mid volume constant electronic bass sound with mid pitch, low volume wavering static tone.

Polyphonic electronic sound which loops on a ~4 second interval from low pitch and low volume to combined low and mid pitch and mid volume. Periodic pop with hard onset and offset, mid pitch and mid volume at the beginning of each loop.
Low pitch, mid volume constant electronic bass sound continues. Wavering static sound has more pronounced fluctuations at mid volume and generally mid pitch.

Avasilichioaei's voice, smooth and clear, with aspirant onset and offset, mid volume and mid pitch. Pauses within phrases and between them. Emphasis on "the subject" and "brute future," which are louder than the surrounding words and uttered with more defined onset.
High volume, harsh windy sound which begins across all pitches, then decreases volume and increases pitch gradually until inaudible.

Avasilichioaei's voice. Repetition of "the subject...," followed by description. Phrases tend to begin with hard onset, mid volume, and clear definition of words, and progress to lower volume and less-defined words, with longer pauses between words.
Muffled mid pitch clicking sound, like ball bearings colliding. Accompanied by low pitch, windy sound. Becomes audible just as Avasilichioaei says the words "laboured hand."
